<div class="desc">
    <div class="container">
        <h2><font color="Black"><b>About WithU</b></font></h2>
        <p><font color="#888888">
    Violence against community nurses is on the rise.<br />
    For community nurses, we are providing you with a platform to:<br />
    Identify the risk level of a patient visit and mitigate the risks;<br />
    Identify potential infectious diseases that patients may be carrying;<br />        
    Help you respond to incidents;<br />
    Let you learn more to protect yourselves.<br />
</font></p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
        <h3 class="text-head"><font color="#1C97CA">Features of WithU<br/><br/></font></h3>
