                    <a href = "/Location_new/Index";><div class="feature-icon icon1" ></div></a>
                    <h4><font color="white"><b>Risk Precaution</b></font></h4>
                    <p><font color="#aab1bf">We will take you through a series of questionnaires, then provide an assessment of your risk profile based on our data, and some recommendations to minimize your risk.</font></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-4" style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px">
                    <a href="/Home/Share_experience" ;><div class="feature-icon icon2"></div></a>
                    <h4><font color="white"><b>Share Experiences</b></font></h4>
                    <p>
                        <font color="#aab1bf">
                           You can share your experiences of visiting patients, and learn how other community nurses deal with violence or aggression.
                        </font>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-6  col-md-4" style="margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:30px">
                    <a href="/Home/protect" ;><div class="feature-icon icon3"></div></a>
                    <h4><font color="white"><b>Protect Yourself</b></font></h4>
                    <p>
                        <font color="#aab1bf">
                            We provide you with information about recognizing violence, self-defense education videos, and how to make claims.
                            So that you can protect yourself against violence and aggression.
                        </font>
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</div>







